HEADWORD: Yojan
<hw>Yo"jan</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Skr.
<ets>y⟦omac⟧jana</ets>.]</ety> <def>A measure of distance, varying from
four to ten miles, but usually about five.</def> <mark>[India]</mark>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>yojana</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

